Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,时间暫停 强暴隔壁人妻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（98堂Artist）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,老公 今晚想吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想 反正时间很多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,汉堡饭呢 有想吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,只要是你做的都好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗 那我就努力咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,早点回来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.64,0:00:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就等着晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,早安 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.72,0:00:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是隔壁邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们隔壁有住人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,搬家那天很吵杂 给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.93,0:01:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,今天休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.93,0:01:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 请好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.27,0:01:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,老公 再不走就要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那我走了\N加油 慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.97,0:01:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一大早就秀恩爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真不顺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那种男人为什么就能娶个美人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:02:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,像我这么老实的就没人多看一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒的屁股 大屁股对着我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,若跟这么好的女人结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,每天都是温柔乡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,原以为晚上能听到精彩的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,连工具都准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,结果自从搬来连一点声响都没
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,该不会老公有性功能障碍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有方法能上那个人妻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有药就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,能暂停时间的摄影机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 能请你在这签名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,签单给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我能不能先确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:03:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,使用说明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,想停止对象的时间就喊暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,停止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒 真的停了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,想恢复的时候就请喊动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 不要闹好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这个好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去下一家送货了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,快滚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有包裹给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,请你签名 好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么让这个派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那样的美女也有性欲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是老公不在 寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,等着 我马上让你开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,隔壁先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,停止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,真的停住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒 这个好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真的停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,停止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的让她停了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真的停了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,胸部好软
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的停了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,还用这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,太太在自慰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这么漂亮的美女也会自慰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.24,0:16:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好下流
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的小穴好下流
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,自慰到一半
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,湿湿的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的淫汁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,太太淫汁流出来了 好下流
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,太太忍很久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我来帮你一点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,太太 亲亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴唇要嘟起来 嘟起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,亲亲 对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:18:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,太太 要好好的看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛睁开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这摄影机太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,太太舌头好软
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,舔舔看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这个好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,胸部也是 胸部也好美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这个胸部好软
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好软
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.73,0:20:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,被暂停了 乳头还硬硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,舔舔看 太太让我舔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:20:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,太太皮肤好滑嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看后面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.04,0:21:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,用搬的真辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.18,0:21:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,脸看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.12,0:22:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.86,0:22:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.93,0:22:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.22,0:22:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真下流的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你自己准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.78,0:23:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.88,0:24:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.61,0:24:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真的停了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.75,0:24:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.56,0:24:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要加入你的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.25,0:25:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这么湿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.53,0:25:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴里面好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.61,0:25:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,湿湿的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.41,0:25:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我要插两根手指
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.29,0:26:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.76,0:26:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.84,0:26:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.45,0:26:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,淫汁好多
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.79,0:26:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,淫汁喷的到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.19,0:26:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.80,0:26:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.27,0:26:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.74,0:26:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这次换这个 我来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.35,0:26:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,转过来这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.90,0:27:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.71,0:27:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.39,0:27:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这身体真让人受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.86,0:27:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,往前一点
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.81,0:28:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,现在就把这个巨根插进去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.36,0:28:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒 这插的好深
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.89,0:28:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,开了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.92,0:28:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.86,0:28:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那么粗的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.39,0:28:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么一下就插进去小穴了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.88,0:29:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的阴唇
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.28,0:29:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是淫汁 超下流
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.22,0:29:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我再快点好了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.76,0:29:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这样才够舒服吧 够舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.97,0:29:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,还是要深点 又深又慢的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.72,0:29:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.32,0:29:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,自己拿着 这样
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.16,0:30:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.06,0:32:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,停止
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.94,0:32:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,太太 不能去喔
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.88,0:32:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.42,0:32:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你自慰真激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.62,0:32:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我想
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.49,0:32:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒一定比这个更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.69,0:32:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.84,0:33:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要用的话
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.98,0:33:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,当然还是肉棒最好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.92,0:33:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,先让你的嘴巴尝尝看
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.41,0:33:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好软
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.21,0:33:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的嘴唇真软
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.90,0:34:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.20,0:34:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好软
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.20,0:34:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,太太嘴巴好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.82,0:34:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.62,0:34:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,太太嘴巴很软 很舒服喔
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.85,0:35:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的手
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.45,0:35:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这样才开心
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.46,0:35:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服喔
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.46,0:35:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.41,0:35:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.88,0:35:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,靠着下巴
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.48,0:35:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴张开 舌头伸长
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.89,0:35:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,再长点
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.43,0:36:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.03,0:36:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,在你脸上
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.30,0:36:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,在你可爱的脸上留下我的精液
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.71,0:36:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好好等着
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.13,0:36:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了...可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.87,0:36:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都给你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.22,0:37:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,看我射好多
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.37,0:37:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.38,0:37:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.01,0:38:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 不睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.28,0:38:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.77,0:38:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,过来这
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.85,0:38:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.97,0:39:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,停止
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.87,0:40:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这么有情调
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.14,0:40:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不顺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.96,0:40:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,太太转过来这
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.38,0:40:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,太太 看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.06,0:41:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我都一直想你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.13,0:41:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,每天都自慰
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.47,0:41:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.81,0:41:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.21,0:41:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.48,0:41:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那我...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.96,0:41:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要好好疼爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.31,0:41:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴唇好软
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.79,0:42:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴嘟起来
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.67,0:42:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嘟
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.87,0:42:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,翘高
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.47,0:42:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这样嘟起来才好亲
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.28,0:42:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.36,0:42:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,又美又软
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.23,0:42:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好软
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.63,0:42:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我要看了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.70,0:42:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.28,0:43:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,果然怎么看都美
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.22,0:43:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头都硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.96,0:43:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这么敏感 有这么舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.43,0:43:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真不顺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.23,0:43:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不顺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.71,0:44:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我要舔胸部了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.46,0:44:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这边也要
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.35,0:44:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.88,0:44:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这么下流 就让你更舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.96,0:44:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,躺着吧 我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.38,0:45:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.64,0:45:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,太太 你的身体真美
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.40,0:45:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,还这么热
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.41,0:45:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,下流
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.54,0:45:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,被我弄兴奋的吧 一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.96,0:46:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好...味道好香
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.43,0:46:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.10,0:46:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看你下流的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.94,0:46:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,居然这么湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.14,0:46:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,太太真下流
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.88,0:47:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,被我弄的 很有感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.02,0:47:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.57,0:47:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,腿好光滑
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.31,0:47:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.08,0:48:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.95,0:48:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,来 把你的脚打开
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.38,0:48:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真美的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.18,0:48:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.19,0:48:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴好嫩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.86,0:48:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,还这么热
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.60,0:49:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,都被我停了身体还那么热
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.22,0:49:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好紧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.24,0:49:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴被我弄的很有感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.65,0:49:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.08,0:50:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好下流
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.55,0:50:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,都这么湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.49,0:50:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好 让你恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.56,0:50:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.63,0:50:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.90,0:50:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.57,0:50:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真性急
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.64,0:50:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,今天表现真大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.31,0:50:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.64,0:50:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,已经脱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.18,0:50:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这么主动
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.65,0:50:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这么想要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.59,0:50:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.73,0:51:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,停止
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.48,0:51:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,谁跟你想要
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.29,0:51:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,当然跟我要
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.43,0:51:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股真美
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.30,0:51:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.11,0:51:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这屁股真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.65,0:51:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,抬高让我看
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.55,0:52:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.95,0:52:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,要舒服的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.83,0:52:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我从后面舔你
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.48,0:53:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.71,0:54:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我都兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.05,0:54:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,都兴奋了 太太
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.96,0:55:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在老公面前吹我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.11,0:55:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴里面好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.12,0:55:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.54,0:55:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 都这么硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.08,0:55:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴里面好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.36,0:56:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,舌头跟脸颊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.56,0:56:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,都给你吹
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.46,0:56:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,在你老公面前 把这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.73,0:56:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,插进里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.40,0:56:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在他面前插
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.27,0:56:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在他面前 插给他看
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.94,0:56:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股抬高趴着
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.61,0:57:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,来趴着
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.18,0:57:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.12,0:57:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴里面好热喔
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.54,0:58:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,比你老公还舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.36,0:58:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的超棒
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.07,0:59:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下去
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.60,1:00:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就保持这样 让你动吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.62,1:00:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,动吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.96,1:00:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好主动
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.50,1:00:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.03,1:00:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,动作真快
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.90,1:00:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你脱的好快
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.11,1:00:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是你自己脱的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.71,1:00:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你都脱了我也脱吧 好
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.12,1:01:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,停止
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.48,1:01:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不是脱给你看的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.83,1:01:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她是脱给我看的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.78,1:01:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,看我这
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.05,1:02:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要舒服的表情 舒服的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.72,1:02:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴张开
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.65,1:02:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢被我插的样子 对
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.19,1:03:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,往他面前做感觉怎样
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.26,1:03:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服就叫出来没关系
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.83,1:03:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,到这边做
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.61,1:04:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.85,1:05:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.84,1:06:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,动吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.71,1:06:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,祥子呢？ 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.71,1:06:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛让我坐在这里
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.85,1:06:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.25,1:06:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚不是说要帮我脱吗
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.60,1:06:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我躺在这什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.40,1:06:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.16,1:07:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,停止
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.63,1:07:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,摸的还真顺手
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.24,1:07:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不乖
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.71,1:07:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样躺着吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.28,1:08:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的小穴好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.09,1:08:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,比他的更棒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.43,1:09:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就给你射在这里
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.22,1:10:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.67,1:11:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的小穴好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.02,1:11:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,动吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.82,1:11:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,祥子
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.55,1:11:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.02,1:11:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是自己上来的 什么
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.76,1:11:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.76,1:11:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我才要问你呢
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.30,1:11:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是搞什么
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.70,1:11:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.90,1:11:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么 不会吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.44,1:11:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经射了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.51,1:11:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有射 我内裤都没脱
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.65,1:11:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.65,1:12:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要不算了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.19,1:12:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,睡吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.15,1:12:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.36,1:12:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.49,1:12:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.63,1:12:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的小穴超舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.23,1:12:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.30,1:12:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,对喔 你不知道 被我暂停了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.24,1:12:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.31,1:13:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这个影片被我朋友看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.25,1:13:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他也想做 虽然很唐突
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.25,1:13:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,请让他插好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.53,1:13:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.54,1:13:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.34,1:13:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,停止
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.36,1:13:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真的停了 对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.16,1:13:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 不会动
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.37,1:14:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,快抱走
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.24,1:14:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,抱进去
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.78,1:14:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好香 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.19,1:14:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没跟这么美的做过
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.93,1:14:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.66,1:14:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.73,1:14:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.60,1:14:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.74,1:14:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.21,1:14:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了 味道好香
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.68,1:14:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这么快就舔了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.42,1:14:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,既然想舔就这样
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.23,1:14:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这样再舔
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.77,1:15:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.65,1:15:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.26,1:15:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,来亲亲
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.93,1:15:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,把她舌头弄出来
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.54,1:15:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这个怎样
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.29,1:16:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我最爱的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.09,1:16:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,老公看到肯定气死了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.76,1:16:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,表情一脸想要的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.51,1:16:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,想不想看内衣 想...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.12,1:16:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,给你见识看看
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.65,1:16:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这太太很棒对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.06,1:16:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.26,1:16:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.53,1:16:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好软
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.27,1:16:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 软绵绵的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.22,1:17:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要夹
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.02,1:17:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我来
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.49,1:17:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这身材真让人受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.17,1:17:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,夹看看
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.04,1:17:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 超想看
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.05,1:17:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看 忍很久了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.79,1:17:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.05,1:17:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,内衣真下流
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.20,1:17:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,想不想看美女人妻的乳头
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.67,1:17:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.07,1:18:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,露乳头了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.08,1:18:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,摸到了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.55,1:18:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 我想这样弄
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.89,1:18:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.70,1:18:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.84,1:18:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样
